text: Flaka Aslanaj (born 14 May 2001) is a Kosovar footballer who plays as a forward and has appeared for the Kosovo women's national team. ==Career== Aslanaj has been capped for the Kosovo national team, appearing for the team during the UEFA Women's Euro 2021 qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:2001 births Category:Living people Category:Kosovan women's footballers Category:Kosovo women's international footballers Category:Women's association football forwards
